- updated API documentation
- CSSOptimizer: cache the images used in the css
- CssOptimizer: update all url declarations in the css so the css works same way on the cached location
- CssOptimizer: using filesystem\Browser to find files on the filesystem
- AbstractOptimizer: cache files to application/public to get a better response time since this directory is directly hosted
- AbstractOptimizer: changed method signature of optimizeSource($source) to optimizeSource($source, File $file)
- AbstractOptimizer: using filesystem\Browser to find files on the filesystem